OL,3,CLiverpool alter their future ticket
OL,4,Cpricing plans after backlash from
OL,5,Csupporters
OL,7,FLiverpool FC have altered their future
OL,8,Fticket pricing plans after a supporter
OL,9,Fbacklash.
OL,11,FThe club announced in March that
OL,12,Fgeneral admission tickets would rise
OL,13,Fwith inflation for the next three
OL,14,Fseasons, after supporters' groups had
OL,15,Fpetitioned for a freeze.
OL,17,FFans have staged protests over the
OL,18,Fplanned approach, and the Reds have
OL,19,Fnow revised plans.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
