FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778181071
OL,3,CLiverpool alter their future ticket
OL,4,Cpricing plans after backlash from
OL,5,Csupporters
OL,7,F"Following further dialogue with its
OL,8,FSupporters Board, the club can now
OL,9,Fconfirm an inflationary increase of
OL,10,Fthree per cent to general admission
OL,11,Ftickets for season 2026-27, followed
OL,12,Fby a price freeze for season 2027-28,"
OL,13,Fa club statement issued on Thursday
OL,14,Fmorning read.
OL,16,F"Further discussions will take place
OL,17,Fwith the Supporters Board for future
OL,18,Fseasons.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@fO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
