OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778181071
OL,3,CLiverpool alter their future ticket
OL,4,Cpricing plans after backlash from
OL,5,Csupporters
OL,7,F"The club and Supporters Board will
OL,8,Fuse the certainty of these seasons to
OL,9,Fseek longer-term alternative solutions
OL,10,Facross the game and explore commercial
OL,11,Fideas with the Supporters Board in an
OL,12,Fattempt to avoid future ticket price
OL,13,Fincreases and address issues around
OL,14,Faffordability and accessibility for
OL,15,Ffuture generations."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
