OL,3,CLiverpool alter their future ticket
OL,4,Cpricing plans after backlash from
OL,5,Csupporters
OL,7,FThe Spirit of Shankly fans' group
OL,8,Fresponded to the news by stating: "We
OL,9,Fwelcome the decision that Liverpool FC
OL,10,Fwill no longer proceed with its
OL,11,Fpreviously announced three-year ticket-
OL,12,Fpricing model.
OL,14,F"Following supporter protests at a
OL,15,Flocked-in multi-year deal and
OL,16,Fconversations with the Supporters'
OL,17,FBoard over the past few days, the club
OL,18,Fhas pledged a new proposal that will
OL,19,Fallow us to examine thoroughly long-
OL,20,Fterm solutions surrounding fan
OL,21,Faffordability and access.
OL,26,@pD@cOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778181071
OL,3,CLiverpool alter their future ticket
OL,4,Cpricing plans after backlash from
OL,5,Csupporters
OL,7,F"We understand disappointment at next
OL,8,Fseason's increase in ticket prices
OL,9,Fwill remain for some, but there will
OL,10,Fbe none the season after and we want
OL,11,Fto assure fans we will continue talks
OL,12,Fwith the club and do our best to find
OL,13,Fother ways to prevent future rises.
OL,15,F"Our matchday culture has also been
OL,16,Ftop of the agenda recently and again,
OL,17,FSOS, as part of the Supporters' Board,
OL,18,Fwill work to protect it.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
