CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778181071
OL,3,CLiverpool alter their future ticket
OL,4,Cpricing plans after backlash from
OL,5,Csupporters
OL,7,F"We would like to thank those at LFC
OL,8,Fwho have listened to us and engaged
OL,9,Fwith us, not all club hierarchies
OL,10,Fwould have done the same. And we look
OL,11,Fforward to working with them to find
OL,12,Ffuture paths that benefit all."
